<%- include('layout', { body: `
<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; align-items: start;">
  <div class="card" style="height: 100%;">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h3>🔗 Pengaturan Threads API</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <form action="/settings/save" method="POST" class="form-stack">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="threads_app_id">Threads App ID</label>
          <input type="text" id="threads_app_id" name="threads_app_id" value="${settings.threads_app_id || ''}" placeholder="Meta App ID">
          <small class="form-hint">App ID dari Meta for Developers untuk semua akun</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="threads_app_secret">Threads App Secret</label>
          <div class="input-with-action">
            <input type="password" id="threads_app_secret" name="threads_app_secret" value="${settings.threads_app_secret || ''}" placeholder="Meta App Secret">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost" onclick="togglePasswordVisibility('threads_app_secret')">👁️</button>
          </div>
          <small class="form-hint">App Secret dari Meta for Developers untuk semua akun</small>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-right-container" style="margin-top: auto;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">💾 Simpan Pengaturan Threads</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="height: 100%;">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h3>🤖 Pengaturan AI (Gemini)</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <form action="/settings/save" method="POST" class="form-stack">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="gemini_api_key">Gemini API Key</label>
          <div class="input-with-action">
            <input type="password" id="gemini_api_key" name="gemini_api_key" value="${settings.gemini_api_key || ''}" placeholder="AIzaSy...">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost" onclick="togglePasswordVisibility('gemini_api_key')">👁️</button>
          </div>
          <small class="form-hint">Dapatkan di <a href="https://aistudio.google.com/apikey" target="_blank">aistudio.google.com</a></small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="gemini_model">Model Gemini</label>
          <select id="gemini_model" name="gemini_model">
            <option value="gemini-2.5-flash" ${settings.gemini_model === 'gemini-2.5-flash' ? 'selected' : ''}>Gemini 2.5 Flash (Default/Fast)</option>
            <option value="gemini-2.5-pro" ${settings.gemini_model === 'gemini-2.5-pro' ? 'selected' : ''}>Gemini 2.5 Pro (Best Quality)</option>
            <option value="gemini-2.0-flash" ${settings.gemini_model === 'gemini-2.0-flash' ? 'selected' : ''}>Gemini 2.0 Flash (Legacy Fast)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-right-container" style="margin-top: auto;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="btn-save-settings">💾 Simpan Pengaturan</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card" id="custom-prompts-card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>✍️ Custom Prompts</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <form action="/settings/save" method="POST" class="form-stack">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="prompt_organic">Prompt untuk Konten Organik</label>
        <textarea id="prompt_organic" name="prompt_organic" rows="12" style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;">${settings.prompt_organic || `Kamu adalah content creator Threads yang viral dengan engagement tinggi di 2026.

Buatkan thread tentang: "{topic}"

Catatan tambahan: {theme_description}

STRUKTUR THREAD (AIDA):

1. MAIN POST (300-400 karakter):
   - HOOK KUAT: Mulai dengan formula viral (specific number, counterintuitive, bold claim, story opener, atau direct callout)
   - Buat knowledge gap (penasaran tapi belum kasih solusi)
   - Gunakan line break untuk readability
   - Front-load value di 3 baris pertama

2. KOMENTAR 1 - Context & Credibility:
   - Jelaskan kenapa topik ini penting
   - Tambahkan relatable pain point atau data spesifik

3. KOMENTAR 2 - Core Value:
   - Deliver insight utama atau solusi konkret
   - Gunakan contoh spesifik atau pengalaman personal

4. KOMENTAR 3 - CTA & Engagement:
   - Personal touch atau hot take
   - AKHIRI dengan pertanyaan spesifik untuk engagement

ATURAN KETAT:
- Bahasa Indonesia casual, conversational, authentic
- Line break setiap 2-3 kalimat
- Emoji: 1-2 per post MAX
- Target 300-400 karakter (max 500)
- NO hashtag, NO clickbait berlebihan
- Fokus conversation over broadcasting

Format output (JSON):
{
  "main_post": "...",
  "comments": ["...", "...", "..."]
}

PENTING: Output HANYA JSON, tanpa markdown atau teks tambahan.`}</textarea>
        <small class="form-hint">Gunakan placeholder: {topic}, {comment_count}, {theme_description}</small>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="prompt_affiliate">Prompt untuk Konten Affiliate</label>
        <textarea id="prompt_affiliate" name="prompt_affiliate" rows="12" style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;">${settings.prompt_affiliate || `Kamu adalah content creator Threads yang ahli soft-selling dengan engagement tinggi di 2026.

Buatkan thread promosi untuk produk affiliate:
- Nama Produk: {product_name}
- Deskripsi: {description}
- Link Affiliate: {affiliate_link}

STRUKTUR THREAD AFFILIATE (AIDA):

1. MAIN POST (300-400 karakter):
   - HOOK SOFT-SELLING: Story opener, transformation, relatable pain, atau counterintuitive
   - JANGAN sebut produk/brand di main post
   - Buat penasaran dengan hasil/benefit
   - Line break untuk readability

2. KOMENTAR 1 - Build Desire:
   - Ceritakan pengalaman personal atau review jujur
   - Fokus ke PROBLEM yang dipecahkan
   - Relatable & authentic

3. KOMENTAR 2 - Reveal Product + Link:
   - Sebutkan nama produk dengan natural
   - Jelaskan 1-2 benefit spesifik
   - Sisipkan link: "Kalau mau cek: [link]"

4. KOMENTAR 3 - Social Proof & CTA:
   - Social proof ringan atau personal insight
   - CTA soft dengan pertanyaan untuk engagement

ATURAN KETAT:
- Bahasa Indonesia casual, authentic
- NO hard selling, NO urgency fake
- Storytelling & soft-selling approach
- Line break setiap 2-3 kalimat
- Emoji: 1-2 per post MAX
- Target 300-400 karakter (max 500)
- NO hashtag

Format output (JSON):
{
  "main_post": "...",
  "comments": ["...", "...", "..."]
}

PENTING: Output HANYA JSON, tanpa markdown atau teks tambahan.`}</textarea>
        <small class="form-hint">Gunakan placeholder: {product_name}, {description}, {affiliate_link}, {comment_count}</small>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="prompt_reply">Prompt untuk Auto Reply</label>
        <textarea id="prompt_reply" name="prompt_reply" rows="8" style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px;">${settings.prompt_reply || `Kamu adalah pemilik akun Threads yang membalas komentar dengan engagement tinggi di 2026.

Konteks postingan: "{post_context}"
Komentar yang perlu dibalas: "{comment}"

ATURAN REPLY VIRAL 2026:

1. GAYA REPLY: {style}

2. STRUKTUR REPLY:
   - Acknowledge komentar mereka (validasi/apresiasi)
   - Tambahkan value baru (insight/perspektif/pertanyaan balik)
   - Buat conversational (bukan robotic)

3. TEKNIK ENGAGEMENT:
   - Gunakan "kamu/lo/kalian" untuk personal connection
   - Kalau mereka bertanya, jawab spesifik + tanya balik
   - Kalau mereka share pengalaman, relate + tambahkan insight
   - Kalau mereka setuju, deepen conversation dengan pertanyaan

4. ATURAN KETAT:
   - Max 150 karakter (singkat & padat)
   - Bahasa Indonesia casual & authentic
   - NO template/robotic response
   - NO emoji berlebihan (max 1)
   - Fokus: continue conversation, bukan close it

Output: HANYA teks reply, tanpa tanda kutip atau format tambahan.`}</textarea>
        <small class="form-hint">Gunakan placeholder: {post_context}, {comment}, {style}</small>
      </div>
      <div class="btn-right-container">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline" onclick="resetPrompts()">🔄 Reset ke Default</button>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">💾 Simpan Custom Prompts</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card" id="auto-reply-settings-card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>💬 Pengaturan Auto Reply</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    ${autoReplyConfigs.length === 0 ? '<p class="empty-state">Belum ada akun terdaftar. <a href="/accounts">Tambah akun</a> terlebih dahulu.</p>' : ''}
    ${autoReplyConfigs.map(config => '<form action="/settings/auto-reply/' + config.account_id + '" method="POST" class="auto-reply-form">' +
      '<div class="auto-reply-header">' +
        '<h4>@' + config.username + '</h4>' +
        '<label class="toggle-switch">' +
          '<input type="checkbox" name="is_enabled" value="1" ' + (config.is_enabled ? 'checked' : '') + '>' +
          '<span class="toggle-slider"></span>' +
          '<span class="toggle-label">' + (config.is_enabled ? 'Aktif' : 'Nonaktif') + '</span>' +
        '</label>' +
      '</div>' +
      '<div class="form-inline-row">' +
        '<div class="form-group" style="flex: 2;"><label>Gaya Reply</label><select name="reply_style">' +
          '<option value="friendly" ' + (config.reply_style === 'friendly' ? 'selected' : '') + '>😊 Friendly</option>' +
          '<option value="witty" ' + (config.reply_style === 'witty' ? 'selected' : '') + '>😄 Witty</option>' +
          '<option value="professional" ' + (config.reply_style === 'professional' ? 'selected' : '') + '>💼 Professional</option>' +
          '<option value="casual" ' + (config.reply_style === 'casual' ? 'selected' : '') + '>😎 Casual</option>' +
        '</select></div>' +
        '<div class="form-group" style="flex: 1;"><label>Max Reply/Check</label><input type="number" name="max_replies_per_check" value="' + (config.max_replies_per_check || 5) + '" min="1" max="20"></div>' +
        '<div><button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="height: 48px; padding: 0 24px;">💾 Simpan</button></div>' +
      '</div>' +
      (config.last_checked_at ? '<small class="form-hint">Last check: ' + config.last_checked_at + '</small>' : '') +
    '</form>').join('<hr>')}
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .card-panduan { grid-column: 1 / -1; width: 100%; }
  .card { margin-bottom: 20px !important; }
  .card:last-child { margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
  .two-column { margin-bottom: 20px !important; }
  .two-column .card { margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
</style>
` }) %>


<script>
function togglePasswordVisibility(inputId) {
  const input = document.getElementById(inputId);
  input.type = input.type === 'password' ? 'text' : 'password';
}

async function resetPrompts() {
  if (!confirm('Reset semua custom prompts ke default?')) return;
  
  document.getElementById('prompt_organic').value = '';
  document.getElementById('prompt_affiliate').value = '';
  document.getElementById('prompt_reply').value = '';
  
  alert('Prompts direset. Klik "Simpan Custom Prompts" untuk menyimpan.');
}
</script>
